709673f-a.title: Manhattan: 7th Avenue - 15th Street
709673f-a.text:
Seventh Avenue, west side, from loth to 15th Streets, showing new apartment house at 200 West loth Street nearing completion.
February 28, 1930.
Charles Curtis.

709672f-a.title: Manhattan: 7th Avenue - 15th Street
709672f-a.text:
Seventh Avenue at N.E. corner of 15th Street, across excavation at
S.W. corner, showing Street and Smith Building.
February 28, 1931.
P.L. Sperr, Photographer.
